---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { seoMetadata } from '../lib/constants';

const pageMetadata = seoMetadata['/mandalafy/'];
---

<BaseLayout title={pageMetadata.title} description={pageMetadata.description}>
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_0.8fr] gap-12 items-center mb-16">
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          Mandalafy
        </h1>

        <p class="text-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
          A digital playground for creating your own mandalas.
        </p>

        <a href="https://mandalafy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors">
          Explore Mandalafy
        </a>
      </div>

      <img
        src="/images/mandala2.webp"
        alt=""
        class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-lg object-cover"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-16">
      <p>
        Mandalafy lets anyone explore a timeless art form through symmetry, color, and curiosity. Draw, experiment, and shape something beautiful—then bring it to life on custom products.
      </p>

      <p>
        What began as a creative experiment grew into a fully interactive digital tool, blending code, design, and accessible creativity into a single, intentional experience.
      </p>

      <p>
        For many people, Mandalafy becomes a moment of flow—a quiet space where intuition and pattern meet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg space-y-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      <p>
        For me, mandalas are more than visual patterns. They’re a creative practice built on rhythm, repetition, and structure.
      </p>

      <p>
        You don’t control every detail. You work within constraints and let the design emerge. Structure provides guidance; creativity fills in the rest.
      </p>

      <p>
        That balance mirrors how I approach digital strategy and systems work.
      </p>

      <p>
        Mandalafy is both a creative offering and a living example of how thoughtful digital environments can feel intuitive, expressive, and human—even when built on complex systems underneath.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>